WEBVTT

00:01:40.180 --> 00:01:44.800
=Love Story in the 1970s=

00:01:45.100 --> 00:01:47.940
=Episode 10=

00:01:47.940 --> 00:01:51.660
(Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory)

00:01:55.330 --> 00:01:57.340
What exactly are you trying to do?

00:01:58.370 --> 00:02:01.670
Fang Muyang refused
to stay home last night.

00:02:01.670 --> 00:02:02.720
He insisted on coming here.

00:02:02.850 --> 00:02:04.420
I tried to stop him, but I couldn't.

00:02:04.420 --> 00:02:05.940
You know

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:07.580
he's still

00:02:08.010 --> 00:02:10.130
not fully recovered.

00:02:10.620 --> 00:02:13.040
If he does something out of line,
that won't be good.

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:14.810
So I had to follow him here.

00:02:14.930 --> 00:02:16.670
You can't sleep here.

00:02:17.160 --> 00:02:18.300
This is the factory office,

00:02:18.460 --> 00:02:19.460
not your home.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:21.040
Pack your things.

00:02:21.460 --> 00:02:22.480
Go. Get out.

00:02:22.480 --> 00:02:23.120
I'm not leaving.

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:25.250
My unit is gone.

00:02:25.460 --> 00:02:26.740
Where do you expect me to go?

00:02:27.510 --> 00:02:29.300
Do you expect us
to sleep on the street?

00:02:30.570 --> 00:02:31.290
Where you sleep

00:02:31.290 --> 00:02:32.220
is none of my concern.

00:02:32.560 --> 00:02:33.960
You can't sleep in the office!

00:02:35.670 --> 00:02:36.180
Feng Lin.

00:02:36.671 --> 00:02:37.700
Throw their bedding out.

00:02:37.960 --> 00:02:39.060
Notify Security.

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:39.980
Have them removed.

00:02:41.220 --> 00:02:41.980
Feng Lin?

00:02:43.130 --> 00:02:44.370
So you're Feng Lin.

00:02:46.182 --> 00:02:47.650
I heard you were assigned housing.

00:02:51.410 --> 00:02:52.900
Ms. Xu once taught me

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:54.810
to put others first.

00:02:55.400 --> 00:02:56.550
You're a college graduate

00:02:57.220 --> 00:02:58.410
and a key member.

00:02:59.337 --> 00:03:00.810
Why don't you show some generosity

00:03:01.250 --> 00:03:02.460
and give us your place?

00:03:07.410 --> 00:03:08.340
Everyone knows

00:03:09.430 --> 00:03:10.440
I had a head injury

00:03:10.740 --> 00:03:12.020
saving you.

00:03:12.293 --> 00:03:13.810
Some days are better, some worse.

00:03:14.850 --> 00:03:15.950
Things from before

00:03:17.090 --> 00:03:18.450
come back to me sometimes.

00:03:19.220 --> 00:03:21.100
I remember that day...

00:03:21.640 --> 00:03:22.530
It was pouring rain.

00:03:25.210 --> 00:03:25.940
Then suddenly,

00:03:27.190 --> 00:03:28.670
lightning split a tree in half.

00:03:29.370 --> 00:03:31.210
And I watched your house collapse.

00:03:32.340 --> 00:03:33.190
What is it?

00:03:34.493 --> 00:03:35.630
(Without the certificate,)

00:03:35.630 --> 00:03:36.720
(we're not legally married.)

00:03:37.250 --> 00:03:38.880
(If anyone sees us sleeping together,)

00:03:38.880 --> 00:03:40.400
it's a conduct problem.

00:03:40.610 --> 00:03:41.980
(We'll both be finished, okay?)

00:03:45.493 --> 00:03:46.820
The moment I walked in, I saw...

00:03:46.820 --> 00:03:47.360
Ms. Xu.

00:03:49.300 --> 00:03:50.340
As a factory officer,

00:03:50.804 --> 00:03:52.110
I should endure hardship first

00:03:52.110 --> 00:03:53.182
and enjoy comfort later.

00:03:53.500 --> 00:03:55.270
I'm willing to give them my unit.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:56.410
I believe

00:03:56.590 --> 00:03:59.370
he needs this place more than I do.

00:04:00.130 --> 00:04:00.960
Feng,

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:02.650
this is...

00:04:06.410 --> 00:04:07.060
Ms. Xu,

00:04:07.650 --> 00:04:09.970
a little hardship on my end is nothing.

00:04:10.880 --> 00:04:11.760
But their action...

00:04:13.540 --> 00:04:14.970
might reflect badly on you.

00:04:15.937 --> 00:04:17.315
I don't want you affected.

00:04:17.940 --> 00:04:18.890
Feng,

00:04:19.280 --> 00:04:20.250
hearing that

00:04:21.420 --> 00:04:22.790
gives me great relief.

00:04:24.980 --> 00:04:25.570
Look at this.

00:04:26.830 --> 00:04:28.150
This is the difference.

00:04:29.210 --> 00:04:31.060
This is what awareness looks like.

00:04:36.990 --> 00:04:37.920
Comrade Feng Lin,

00:04:40.730 --> 00:04:41.630
thank you.

00:04:57.540 --> 00:04:59.060
(When our comrades face difficulties,)

00:04:59.060 --> 00:05:00.715
(see the achievements,
see the light,)

00:05:00.737 --> 00:05:01.660
(and raise our courage.)

00:05:02.540 --> 00:05:03.560
Fine. You can stay.

00:05:03.770 --> 00:05:04.940
Go ahead, stay!

00:05:05.180 --> 00:05:06.180
So be it!

00:05:07.250 --> 00:05:08.420
Let's see how you manage!

00:05:12.540 --> 00:05:13.800
Let's see how you manage!

00:05:13.980 --> 00:05:16.210
Feng Lin, what are you doing?

00:05:19.080 --> 00:05:20.540
I may have given you the unit,

00:05:21.130 --> 00:05:23.010
but I painted these walls myself.

00:05:23.010 --> 00:05:24.271
I'll paint them however I want!

00:05:25.250 --> 00:05:26.350
This is our place.

00:05:26.350 --> 00:05:27.430
Feng Lin, don't push it.

00:05:27.430 --> 00:05:28.250
I don't care!

00:05:30.330 --> 00:05:32.330
I just won't let you have it easy.

00:05:32.950 --> 00:05:33.810
Feng Lin.

00:05:34.980 --> 00:05:35.680
Feng Lin!

00:05:40.450 --> 00:05:41.130
Feng Lin.

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:43.630
I'll say this one last time.

00:05:44.980 --> 00:05:46.980
I'm only taking back what's mine.

00:05:47.820 --> 00:05:48.680
As long as you stop

00:05:48.782 --> 00:05:49.980
giving Fei Ni a hard time,

00:05:51.426 --> 00:05:53.130
the things I'm not supposed to remember

00:05:56.060 --> 00:05:57.420
will be forgotten completely.

00:06:00.450 --> 00:06:01.660
Why should I believe you?

00:06:02.610 --> 00:06:03.810
You don't have a choice.

00:06:12.210 --> 00:06:13.010
Let her go.

00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:28.010
I've got an idea.

00:06:29.020 --> 00:06:30.010
Let's buy something.

00:06:32.940 --> 00:06:34.650
I've been meaning to ask.

00:06:35.430 --> 00:06:37.200
Why is Feng Lin so afraid of you?

00:06:38.770 --> 00:06:39.660
Don't ask.

00:06:40.210 --> 00:06:41.520
We got the unit back anyway.

00:06:53.270 --> 00:06:53.980
Don't be nervous.

00:06:54.180 --> 00:06:55.250
My parents are easygoing.

00:06:57.740 --> 00:06:58.420
Dad.

00:06:58.500 --> 00:06:59.120
Mom.

00:06:59.870 --> 00:07:00.570
You're back.

00:07:01.080 --> 00:07:02.010
Good, good.

00:07:02.870 --> 00:07:03.920
This is Fang Mujing.

00:07:04.130 --> 00:07:04.940
Dad, Mom.

00:07:05.870 --> 00:07:06.810
Don't just stand there.

00:07:06.810 --> 00:07:08.110
Take Jing to wash her hands.

00:07:08.110 --> 00:07:09.200
Dinner's ready.

00:07:09.200 --> 00:07:09.770
Go on.

00:07:10.010 --> 00:07:10.640
Yes, go on.

00:07:14.220 --> 00:07:17.260
(Qu Xueli, Gu Aizhen)

00:07:20.940 --> 00:07:21.600
Fang,

00:07:22.140 --> 00:07:24.640
Qu Hua has always
been a level-headed person.

00:07:25.260 --> 00:07:26.940
For him to suddenly start seeing you,

00:07:27.700 --> 00:07:30.260
and then suddenly say
he wants to marry you,

00:07:31.940 --> 00:07:33.020
to be honest,

00:07:33.280 --> 00:07:35.790
his father and I
were a little surprised.

00:07:36.990 --> 00:07:39.450
But after meeting you today,

00:07:41.290 --> 00:07:42.940
I think I understand him now.

00:07:52.140 --> 00:07:53.620
Today is a happy day.

00:07:54.090 --> 00:07:56.060
Qu Hua, I give you my blessing.

00:07:56.330 --> 00:07:57.530
From today on,

00:07:58.330 --> 00:07:59.850
you are revolutionary partners.

00:08:00.090 --> 00:08:01.820
In your future work

00:08:01.970 --> 00:08:03.090
and in life,

00:08:03.330 --> 00:08:04.940
you must support and love each other,

00:08:05.410 --> 00:08:06.450
and grow old together.

00:08:07.290 --> 00:08:09.090
Come, let's raise a glass.

00:08:09.090 --> 00:08:09.720
Fang,

00:08:10.140 --> 00:08:13.230
on behalf of Qu Hua's father
and myself,

00:08:13.410 --> 00:08:15.740
welcome to our family.

00:08:17.190 --> 00:08:17.580
Come.

00:08:19.700 --> 00:08:21.210
Thank you, Dad. Thank you, Mom.

00:08:48.100 --> 00:08:48.930
Dad, Mom,

00:08:49.290 --> 00:08:50.290
after we're married,

00:08:50.460 --> 00:08:51.620
I'll fulfill my duties

00:08:51.620 --> 00:08:52.650
as a wife.

00:08:58.260 --> 00:08:59.050
Good.

00:09:01.100 --> 00:09:01.740
Qu Hua,

00:09:02.290 --> 00:09:03.050
Grandma's awake.

00:09:06.290 --> 00:09:07.100
Grandma.

00:09:08.260 --> 00:09:10.260
(Jiang Fengying)

00:09:11.860 --> 00:09:13.650
Hua, you're back.

00:09:15.860 --> 00:09:17.100
You've gotten thinner.

00:09:18.100 --> 00:09:19.620
Thinner is good. I look sharp.

00:09:20.980 --> 00:09:21.570
Grandma.

00:09:23.140 --> 00:09:24.020
I'm married now.

00:09:26.460 --> 00:09:27.790
I know, I know.

00:09:27.980 --> 00:09:28.930
Marriage is good.

00:09:28.930 --> 00:09:30.870
Now, I can have peace of mind.

00:09:31.400 --> 00:09:33.220
This is my wife, Fang Mujing.

00:09:35.890 --> 00:09:36.930
Hello, Grandma.

00:09:43.650 --> 00:09:44.260
Mom,

00:09:44.930 --> 00:09:46.260
we don't really do this anymore.

00:09:47.170 --> 00:09:48.460
Her mind isn't very clear.

00:09:48.460 --> 00:09:49.250
Just let her be.

00:09:49.620 --> 00:09:50.860
I've kept this red envelope

00:09:51.240 --> 00:09:53.410
ready for you all this time.

00:09:54.100 --> 00:09:54.980
Yan,

00:09:55.340 --> 00:09:57.930
now that you've finally married Hua,

00:09:58.290 --> 00:09:59.740
I am so happy.

00:09:59.740 --> 00:10:01.340
Here, take it.

00:10:01.980 --> 00:10:02.770
It's for you.

00:10:08.620 --> 00:10:11.290
Yan, take it.

00:10:15.410 --> 00:10:16.050
Grandma,

00:10:17.050 --> 00:10:18.220
my name is Fang Mujing.

00:10:21.100 --> 00:10:22.740
Alright. Take it.

00:10:27.740 --> 00:10:28.530
Take it.

00:10:31.260 --> 00:10:32.100
Grandma,

00:10:32.340 --> 00:10:33.140
we'll accept it.

00:10:33.340 --> 00:10:34.100
Thank you, Grandma.

00:10:34.100 --> 00:10:35.340
Good.

00:10:35.860 --> 00:10:36.390
Jiang.

00:10:36.390 --> 00:10:37.050
Stand up now.

00:10:37.380 --> 00:10:38.650
Wheel Grandma over for dinner.

00:10:38.650 --> 00:10:39.230
Okay.

00:10:50.380 --> 00:10:50.910
Let's eat.

00:10:51.000 --> 00:10:51.530
Slowly.

00:10:52.100 --> 00:10:53.500
Jiang, get a pair of chopsticks.

00:10:53.570 --> 00:10:54.030
Sure.

00:11:00.100 --> 00:11:01.080
Are you splashing it?

00:11:01.290 --> 00:11:02.100
Yeah.

00:11:02.410 --> 00:11:04.030
But this is our wall now.

00:11:04.340 --> 00:11:05.160
Trust me on this.

00:11:07.100 --> 00:11:09.910
Let's go. Three, two, one.

00:11:17.780 --> 00:11:23.820
♪If the future cannot be touched♪

00:11:24.580 --> 00:11:27.820
♪Don't think too far ahead♪

00:11:27.860 --> 00:11:31.220
♪Just work hard for today♪

00:11:31.620 --> 00:11:34.900
♪Learn from the sun, how warm it is♪

00:11:35.060 --> 00:11:38.820
♪Light up the corners that need it♪

00:11:38.940 --> 00:11:41.740
♪The ones who smile the most♪

00:11:41.820 --> 00:11:44.100
♪Gain the most in return♪

00:11:45.300 --> 00:11:48.700
♪I want a life that's real♪

00:11:48.780 --> 00:11:52.180
♪Steady, feet on solid ground♪

00:11:52.420 --> 00:11:55.820
♪Slowly, our paths begin to cross♪

00:11:55.940 --> 00:11:59.140
♪Each day holds
something to look forward to♪

00:11:59.300 --> 00:12:02.540
♪I want a life that's real♪

00:12:03.890 --> 00:12:05.890
Well? Did you get the hang of it?

00:12:06.860 --> 00:12:07.690
Yeah.

00:12:09.020 --> 00:12:09.860
Draw one.

00:12:09.860 --> 00:12:11.860
♪Making them into memories♪

00:12:19.260 --> 00:12:20.290
How does it look?

00:12:23.000 --> 00:12:24.070
A bit problematic.

00:12:25.020 --> 00:12:25.800
Look over here.

00:12:57.660 --> 00:13:02.460
♪After the laughter, I think of you♪

00:13:04.780 --> 00:13:09.540
♪After the storm, I think of you♪

00:13:11.580 --> 00:13:14.340
♪In the little courtyard♪

00:13:14.380 --> 00:13:17.740
♪There you are dancing♪

00:13:18.700 --> 00:13:23.420
♪That earnest you,
smiling so innocently♪

00:13:25.820 --> 00:13:30.660
♪In spring, I stay by your side♪

00:13:32.820 --> 00:13:37.580
♪When summer comes, I watch over you♪

00:13:39.980 --> 00:13:42.820
♪The fallen leaves in autumn♪

00:13:42.900 --> 00:13:46.300
♪You belong to me♪

00:13:46.780 --> 00:13:50.540
♪When the world is covered in snow♪

00:13:50.620 --> 00:13:55.460
♪I still think of you♪

00:14:00.500 --> 00:14:03.020
(Spring breeze drifts over the hills,)

00:14:03.930 --> 00:14:06.340
(delivering warmth to the window.)

00:14:07.770 --> 00:14:09.860
(Willow branches dip into the river,)

00:14:10.340 --> 00:14:13.340
(scattering green along the banks.)

00:14:14.460 --> 00:14:16.340
(Golden fields of rapeseed flowers)

00:14:16.770 --> 00:14:18.800
(are stamps pressed down by the sun.)

00:14:20.260 --> 00:14:20.920
Lin Mei,

00:14:21.170 --> 00:14:22.220
my request was approved.

00:14:22.650 --> 00:14:23.530
I'm going home.

00:14:23.650 --> 00:14:24.740
I'm going home!

00:14:24.740 --> 00:14:25.860
I'm finally going home!

00:14:27.260 --> 00:14:29.650
(Dandelions open their tiny umbrellas,)

00:14:30.170 --> 00:14:32.980
(carrying news
of spring to distant lands.)

00:14:33.740 --> 00:14:35.860
(See the sunlight blanket the earth,)

00:14:36.570 --> 00:14:37.980
(grass lush and green,)

00:14:38.500 --> 00:14:39.890
(and wildflowers in full bloom.)

00:14:40.690 --> 00:14:43.980
(The whole spring blossoms just for me.)

00:14:46.420 --> 00:14:49.860
♪Remember, that's me♪

00:14:51.380 --> 00:14:53.980
♪Thinking of you♪

00:14:53.980 --> 00:14:55.900
(Spring breeze drifts over the hills,
delivering warmth to the window.)

00:14:55.900 --> 00:14:57.700
(Willow branches dip into the river,
scattering green along the banks.)

00:14:57.700 --> 00:14:59.650
(Golden fields of rapeseed flowers
are stamps pressed down by the sun.)

00:14:59.650 --> 00:15:00.600
(Dandelions open their tiny umbrellas,)

00:15:00.600 --> 00:15:01.910
(carrying news
of spring to distant lands.)

00:15:01.910 --> 00:15:03.600
(See the sunlight blanket the earth,
grass lush and green,)

00:15:03.600 --> 00:15:04.300
(and wildflowers in full bloom.)

00:15:04.300 --> 00:15:05.700
(The whole spring blossoms just for me.)

00:15:29.650 --> 00:15:31.500
Are you getting used
to the things I bought?

00:15:33.220 --> 00:15:34.530
I'm not very good at shopping.

00:15:36.810 --> 00:15:38.500
The "Yan" Grandma kept calling,

00:15:39.340 --> 00:15:41.010
was that your ex-girlfriend?

00:15:53.470 --> 00:15:56.140
Grandma has a malignant brain tumor.

00:15:56.860 --> 00:15:58.500
It's pressing on her nerves.

00:15:58.930 --> 00:16:01.050
That's why she mistook you for her.

00:16:04.620 --> 00:16:06.530
Did Grandma mistake me for someone else,

00:16:07.180 --> 00:16:08.950
or did you choose me because

00:16:08.950 --> 00:16:09.650
I look like her?

00:16:22.493 --> 00:16:25.100
I don't want a lie that falls apart
the second I question it.

00:16:34.860 --> 00:16:35.650
Yes.

00:16:36.570 --> 00:16:37.740
I proposed to you

00:16:38.340 --> 00:16:41.050
because you look like Yan.

00:16:53.100 --> 00:16:53.890
So,

00:16:55.340 --> 00:16:56.890
Professor Wu knew Yan, too?

00:16:58.650 --> 00:17:00.460
Professor Wu is Yan's uncle.

00:17:09.290 --> 00:17:10.130
No wonder.

00:17:11.290 --> 00:17:12.850
He kept hinting

00:17:13.260 --> 00:17:14.900
that I should learn about your past.

00:17:15.810 --> 00:17:16.740
But he wouldn't

00:17:16.740 --> 00:17:18.080
say it outright.

00:17:19.660 --> 00:17:20.610
In his eyes,

00:17:20.940 --> 00:17:22.850
I'm just a pathetic substitute

00:17:23.740 --> 00:17:25.570
who is still smugly thinking

00:17:25.850 --> 00:17:27.740
that I'd found love.

00:17:32.740 --> 00:17:33.530
Fang Mujing,

00:17:34.850 --> 00:17:37.500
did you say yes to my proposal for love?

00:17:39.530 --> 00:17:40.460
Or was it

00:17:40.460 --> 00:17:42.260
to escape your family background?

00:17:45.130 --> 00:17:47.900
You confirmed
our relationship one minute,

00:17:47.900 --> 00:17:49.740
and the next,

00:17:49.740 --> 00:17:52.740
you rushed to submit your application
to join the project team.

00:17:53.810 --> 00:17:55.330
How much of that urgency

00:17:55.330 --> 00:17:57.130
was really about love?

00:18:01.740 --> 00:18:03.900
If my father weren't
a revolutionary soldier,

00:18:05.020 --> 00:18:06.610
would you still have married me?

00:18:16.900 --> 00:18:18.810
If I didn't look like Yan,

00:18:19.850 --> 00:18:21.130
would you still have married me?

00:18:30.740 --> 00:18:32.330
Since we're both getting what we need,

00:18:33.090 --> 00:18:34.610
let's not pretend it's love.

00:18:35.330 --> 00:18:37.090
You come from a top cadre family.

00:18:37.330 --> 00:18:39.740
You have no idea what injustice
and humiliation feel like.

00:18:40.330 --> 00:18:41.130
My family background

00:18:41.850 --> 00:18:43.090
is like a birthmark on my face.

00:18:43.090 --> 00:18:44.610
People always see it.

00:18:44.810 --> 00:18:47.130
It's constantly
reminding me and everyone else

00:18:47.130 --> 00:18:48.420
that I'm inferior.

00:18:49.460 --> 00:18:50.700
No matter how hard I try,

00:18:50.940 --> 00:18:53.460
I can't have
what others reach without effort.

00:18:54.500 --> 00:18:55.290
You're right.

00:18:55.810 --> 00:18:56.940
I was quick to use

00:18:56.940 --> 00:18:58.220
the Qu family name.

00:18:58.530 --> 00:19:00.290
But I will also do my part,

00:19:01.130 --> 00:19:02.940
and be a proper wife.

00:19:03.940 --> 00:19:05.740
Do you think the way you're acting now

00:19:07.130 --> 00:19:08.740
is what a proper wife looks like?

00:19:09.610 --> 00:19:10.460
Of course.

00:19:13.850 --> 00:19:16.020
I can play Yan's stand-in just fine.

00:19:40.130 --> 00:19:41.090
Between her and me,

00:19:42.530 --> 00:19:43.850
who has the better figure?

00:19:49.090 --> 00:19:49.740
What?

00:19:50.370 --> 00:19:52.020
You can treat me like her substitute,

00:19:52.940 --> 00:19:54.530
but you won't let me mention her?

00:20:32.182 --> 00:20:33.770
I'll sleep at the hospital tonight.

00:21:03.860 --> 00:21:09.660
(Staff Canteen)

00:21:16.740 --> 00:21:17.840
Mr. Li.

00:21:18.130 --> 00:21:19.220
Two extra pieces of meat.

00:21:19.770 --> 00:21:20.340
Alright.

00:21:25.180 --> 00:21:26.130
Don't tell anyone.

00:21:26.290 --> 00:21:27.090
Okay.

00:21:37.090 --> 00:21:37.700
Fei Ni!

00:21:38.660 --> 00:21:39.130
Ms. Liu.

00:21:40.530 --> 00:21:40.940
Here.

00:21:42.290 --> 00:21:43.090
Have some meat.

00:21:43.660 --> 00:21:44.530
Thanks, Ms. Liu.

00:21:44.570 --> 00:21:45.610
Don't mention it.

00:21:45.610 --> 00:21:46.260
Fei Ni,

00:21:46.370 --> 00:21:47.220
congratulations.

00:21:48.980 --> 00:21:51.050
I was wondering
how you could even turn down

00:21:51.050 --> 00:21:52.090
someone like Ye Feng.

00:21:52.770 --> 00:21:54.530
You had Fang Muyang as your fallback.

00:21:56.900 --> 00:21:59.740
Fang Muyang may not
have Ye Feng's prospects,

00:21:59.740 --> 00:22:00.530
but

00:22:00.530 --> 00:22:04.530
Ye Feng's temper was spoiled rotten
by that certain someone.

00:22:05.130 --> 00:22:06.980
You were right to break up with him.

00:22:08.570 --> 00:22:10.680
Ms. Liu,
Fang Muyang isn't my fallback.

00:22:11.050 --> 00:22:11.980
Besides,

00:22:12.370 --> 00:22:14.330
I don't think Fang Muyang is
worse than Ye Feng.

00:22:16.330 --> 00:22:16.980
Right.

00:22:16.980 --> 00:22:17.850
I get it.

00:22:18.090 --> 00:22:18.980
My mistake.

00:22:18.980 --> 00:22:19.940
That's on me.

00:22:22.460 --> 00:22:23.530
Come to think of it,

00:22:24.337 --> 00:22:26.770
you and Fang Muyang already
got your marriage certificate.

00:22:27.050 --> 00:22:29.090
When are you treating us
to wedding candy?

00:22:31.740 --> 00:22:32.570
He's not so stingy

00:22:32.570 --> 00:22:34.370
that he won't even buy candy, is he?

00:22:35.370 --> 00:22:36.050
Or

00:22:36.448 --> 00:22:38.130
is it because he doesn't have a job yet

00:22:38.500 --> 00:22:39.530
and can't afford it?

00:22:39.530 --> 00:22:40.900
No, of course not.

00:22:40.900 --> 00:22:41.500
Then why?

00:22:41.500 --> 00:22:42.604
I told him not to buy any.

00:22:44.370 --> 00:22:46.980
I think it's a waste of money.

00:22:48.770 --> 00:22:50.370
That's just being naïve.

00:22:50.980 --> 00:22:52.370
Getting married is a big deal.

00:22:52.370 --> 00:22:54.900
If you won't even
give out wedding candy,

00:22:55.530 --> 00:22:56.660
people are bound

00:22:57.370 --> 00:22:59.330
to talk behind your backs.

00:22:59.660 --> 00:23:00.770
Let them talk.

00:23:00.770 --> 00:23:01.660
I don't care.

00:23:01.660 --> 00:23:02.850
I'm not afraid to face them.

00:23:04.370 --> 00:23:05.700
Honestly, you...

00:23:05.840 --> 00:23:06.940
- You're now...
- Ms. Liu.

00:23:07.290 --> 00:23:09.260
Notify all married comrades
in Workshop One

00:23:09.260 --> 00:23:11.370
to gather outside
the factory office at one o'clock.

00:23:11.810 --> 00:23:12.530
Alright, alright.

00:23:13.940 --> 00:23:15.460
Let's go together after lunch.

00:23:16.130 --> 00:23:16.700
Me?

00:23:19.530 --> 00:23:21.940
You're a married comrade now too.

00:23:23.810 --> 00:23:24.370
Right.

00:23:26.700 --> 00:23:33.860
(Strive to Be the Best)

00:23:34.460 --> 00:23:35.130
Ms. Liu,

00:23:35.460 --> 00:23:37.180
what are they handing out?

00:23:37.180 --> 00:23:38.570
Work safety supplies?

00:23:39.700 --> 00:23:40.940
Safety supplies?

00:23:41.770 --> 00:23:43.050
Contraceptives.

00:23:45.460 --> 00:23:46.770
I don't need that.

00:23:48.130 --> 00:23:48.500
Fei Ni!

00:23:49.260 --> 00:23:50.460
What are you doing?

00:23:50.460 --> 00:23:52.050
We finally made it to the front.

00:23:52.700 --> 00:23:53.530
Fei Ni,

00:23:54.040 --> 00:23:54.750
don't tell me

00:23:54.750 --> 00:23:56.850
you're already planning to get pregnant.

00:23:57.530 --> 00:24:01.700
We can handle contraception ourselves.

00:24:01.700 --> 00:24:02.500
No, no.

00:24:04.770 --> 00:24:05.900
Comrade Fei Ni,

00:24:06.260 --> 00:24:07.900
don't overestimate yourself.

00:24:08.660 --> 00:24:10.330
You young people

00:24:10.460 --> 00:24:12.420
always think you can count the days,

00:24:12.420 --> 00:24:13.960
that you know what you're doing.

00:24:15.770 --> 00:24:16.850
Let me tell you,

00:24:17.420 --> 00:24:19.660
when things get heated,

00:24:19.940 --> 00:24:22.050
all that planning goes out the window.

00:24:24.850 --> 00:24:26.420
So I'm telling you,

00:24:26.420 --> 00:24:29.770
no amount of guesswork beats science.

00:24:32.940 --> 00:24:34.180
Let's go.

00:24:34.940 --> 00:24:38.060
(Family Planning Office)

00:24:38.060 --> 00:24:41.020
(Jiangcheng Daily)

00:24:42.020 --> 00:24:43.530
I've read your article.

00:24:43.530 --> 00:24:44.330
It's good.

00:24:45.850 --> 00:24:49.020
After you graduate,
come work at the paper.

00:24:49.020 --> 00:24:50.260
Thank you, Uncle Fu.

00:24:50.260 --> 00:24:51.420
I'll keep working hard.

00:24:51.660 --> 00:24:52.460
Uncle Fu,

00:24:53.130 --> 00:24:53.940
I...

00:24:55.460 --> 00:24:56.220
Class is over?

00:24:57.260 --> 00:24:58.940
Ling Yi's here, too.

00:24:58.940 --> 00:25:01.420
You two haven't
seen each other in a while, right?

00:25:03.130 --> 00:25:03.850
Uncle Fu,

00:25:04.610 --> 00:25:06.370
I came to tell you something.

00:25:07.220 --> 00:25:08.220
I'm married.

00:25:08.530 --> 00:25:09.740
What?

00:25:10.020 --> 00:25:11.330
You're married?

00:25:11.530 --> 00:25:12.020
Yes.

00:25:12.460 --> 00:25:13.260
When was that?

00:25:13.660 --> 00:25:14.420
To whom?

00:25:14.740 --> 00:25:15.460
Fei Ni.

00:25:15.740 --> 00:25:17.020
She's been taking care of me.

00:25:18.850 --> 00:25:20.420
That's wonderful news.

00:25:20.420 --> 00:25:21.980
Finally, someone can keep you in line.

00:25:22.530 --> 00:25:23.330
Don't forget

00:25:23.330 --> 00:25:25.980
to bring your wife over sometime.

00:25:25.980 --> 00:25:27.740
Let my wife and I meet her properly.

00:25:27.850 --> 00:25:28.530
Sure.

00:25:29.020 --> 00:25:30.370
Fei Ni loves good food.

00:25:30.740 --> 00:25:32.660
Have Ms. Liu cook her something nice.

00:25:32.770 --> 00:25:34.050
Look at you.

00:25:34.050 --> 00:25:36.770
You're already doting on your wife.

00:25:37.370 --> 00:25:41.120
Don't worry.
She will make braised pork ribs.

00:25:41.120 --> 00:25:43.020
That's her specialty.

00:25:43.020 --> 00:25:43.570
Great.

00:25:43.980 --> 00:25:45.530
I'll thank her for Fei Ni in advance.

00:25:45.770 --> 00:25:47.370
You just won't stop saying her name.

00:25:47.740 --> 00:25:48.770
Now I'm curious.

00:25:48.850 --> 00:25:50.260
What kind of magic does she have

00:25:50.260 --> 00:25:53.050
to tame a little rascal like you?

00:25:53.493 --> 00:25:54.770
You'll see when you meet her.

00:25:55.460 --> 00:25:56.260
I should get going.

00:25:56.260 --> 00:25:57.626
Fei Ni's waiting for me at home.

00:25:57.660 --> 00:25:58.530
See you, Uncle Fu.

00:25:59.740 --> 00:26:01.660
Next time, bring your wife.

00:26:01.660 --> 00:26:02.460
Definitely.

00:26:02.770 --> 00:26:03.500
Goodbye.

00:26:06.260 --> 00:26:08.770
He really caught me off guard.

00:26:11.020 --> 00:26:11.850
Uncle Fu,

00:26:13.330 --> 00:26:13.770
I...

00:26:14.020 --> 00:26:14.940
I'll get going, too.

00:26:18.140 --> 00:26:20.020
(Jiangcheng Daily)

00:26:20.020 --> 00:26:20.850
Fang Muyang.

00:26:24.850 --> 00:26:25.660
What is it?

00:26:28.260 --> 00:26:29.020
Do you...

00:26:32.850 --> 00:26:33.940
Do you hate me?

00:26:35.810 --> 00:26:36.980
Why would I hate you?

00:26:39.850 --> 00:26:41.570
I didn't visit you at the hospital

00:26:41.810 --> 00:26:44.260
because I was out on assignment.

00:26:44.370 --> 00:26:46.090
I did plan to go, but...

00:26:46.090 --> 00:26:46.970
You need not explain.

00:26:48.260 --> 00:26:49.810
You weren't obligated
to look after me.

00:26:51.093 --> 00:26:52.260
In fact, I should thank you.

00:26:52.870 --> 00:26:53.850
If you had come,

00:26:54.160 --> 00:26:55.290
Fei Ni wouldn't have.

00:26:55.610 --> 00:26:56.850
We wouldn't have gotten married.

00:27:03.740 --> 00:27:05.290
Your memory's fully back?

00:27:07.850 --> 00:27:08.980
In my memory,

00:27:10.260 --> 00:27:11.810
we were just childhood friends.

00:27:12.660 --> 00:27:13.850
You were never my girlfriend.

00:27:15.130 --> 00:27:15.770
As for why

00:27:15.770 --> 00:27:17.180
I gave you my university spot,

00:27:18.020 --> 00:27:19.330
you know it better than I do.

00:27:22.940 --> 00:27:23.610
Ling Yi,

00:27:24.370 --> 00:27:26.260
whatever you once felt for me,

00:27:27.660 --> 00:27:28.770
now that you've

00:27:29.260 --> 00:27:30.610
chosen a different path,

00:27:31.420 --> 00:27:33.020
you should put your heart

00:27:33.420 --> 00:27:34.810
into that choice.

00:27:36.850 --> 00:27:38.260
And besides, I married Fei Ni.

00:27:39.260 --> 00:27:40.760
Shouldn't that make you happy?

00:27:45.120 --> 00:27:46.400
I am happy.

00:27:46.980 --> 00:27:48.660
That's one less rival.

00:27:49.420 --> 00:27:51.020
After all,

00:27:51.370 --> 00:27:52.740
Ye Feng is what matters most to me.

00:28:05.370 --> 00:28:06.515
Where are you taking me?

00:28:06.900 --> 00:28:07.900
Come on, get up.

00:28:08.530 --> 00:28:09.130
Careful.

00:28:23.260 --> 00:28:26.020
You can actually
come up to this rooftop?

00:28:28.260 --> 00:28:29.460
I just found out, too.

00:28:36.020 --> 00:28:37.050
Here, climb up.

00:28:46.850 --> 00:28:48.610
It's beautiful.

00:29:09.460 --> 00:29:10.080
Sit down.

00:29:21.330 --> 00:29:23.050
I really love this home.

00:29:23.830 --> 00:29:25.330
I really do.

00:29:28.050 --> 00:29:28.850
Fang Muyang,

00:29:29.980 --> 00:29:31.420
we finally have a home.

00:29:31.940 --> 00:29:34.530
But it's completely empty right now.

00:29:34.660 --> 00:29:36.660
We need to fill it with furniture.

00:29:37.810 --> 00:29:39.370
The unit is yours.

00:29:40.050 --> 00:29:42.810
I'll cover a bit more
of the furniture costs.

00:29:43.740 --> 00:29:44.770
I did the math.

00:29:45.330 --> 00:29:47.500
Buying secondhand

00:29:47.610 --> 00:29:48.420
is the best deal.

00:29:49.570 --> 00:29:50.570
I'm fine with anything.

00:29:51.260 --> 00:29:52.610
But I can't let you use secondhand.

00:29:53.420 --> 00:29:54.660
Why not?

00:29:55.293 --> 00:29:56.370
As long as it's cheap.

00:29:57.180 --> 00:29:58.660
Don't worry about the furniture.

00:29:58.740 --> 00:29:59.530
Leave it to me.

00:30:01.360 --> 00:30:02.610
The money your sister gave you

00:30:02.610 --> 00:30:04.050
is almost gone.

00:30:04.180 --> 00:30:06.220
You still need to buy brushes and paper.

00:30:06.660 --> 00:30:07.940
You should save where you can.

00:30:08.850 --> 00:30:10.610
Who knows when you'll start earning?

00:30:11.700 --> 00:30:12.260
Oh, right.

00:30:16.940 --> 00:30:18.260
I bought you a new pen.

00:30:20.130 --> 00:30:20.900
What's this?

00:30:22.580 --> 00:30:23.980
(Condoms)

00:30:24.420 --> 00:30:24.900
This...

00:30:26.020 --> 00:30:28.260
It's nothing. Give it to me.

00:30:30.000 --> 00:30:31.300
Give it back.

00:30:32.330 --> 00:30:33.180
Fang Muyang!

00:30:33.180 --> 00:30:34.337
- You don't know?
- Stop it.

00:30:34.782 --> 00:30:35.420
You don't know?

00:30:35.420 --> 00:30:37.180
I'll go ask our parents later.

00:30:37.330 --> 00:30:38.530
Give it to me.

00:30:39.460 --> 00:30:39.910
You...

00:30:45.400 --> 00:30:46.740
Are you done? Give it back.

00:30:46.740 --> 00:30:47.150
It was

00:30:47.740 --> 00:30:48.900
handed out at the factory.

00:31:10.260 --> 00:31:12.260
It's already dinner time. Where's Fang?

00:31:12.740 --> 00:31:13.530
I'm here, Dad.

00:31:13.950 --> 00:31:15.180
Let's add another dish.

00:31:17.740 --> 00:31:18.700
You bought all this?

00:31:18.700 --> 00:31:19.280
Yeah.

00:31:19.980 --> 00:31:21.570
I wanted some pork belly,
but I'm out of

00:31:21.570 --> 00:31:22.570
meat coupons this month.

00:31:23.420 --> 00:31:24.050
Mom,

00:31:24.770 --> 00:31:26.290
I'll buy pork belly next month.

00:31:26.290 --> 00:31:27.570
Make us some braised pork then?

00:31:27.740 --> 00:31:28.500
Sure.

00:31:29.770 --> 00:31:31.240
The month's barely started

00:31:31.240 --> 00:31:32.604
and you've used up your coupons?

00:31:33.660 --> 00:31:34.700
We're newlyweds.

00:31:34.700 --> 00:31:35.770
We should celebrate.

00:31:36.048 --> 00:31:36.920
When it comes to food,

00:31:36.920 --> 00:31:38.260
you can come up with any excuse.

00:31:39.570 --> 00:31:40.570
Alright, alright.

00:31:41.130 --> 00:31:42.660
Fang did this for you.

00:31:42.660 --> 00:31:44.290
You've been exhausted
fixing up the unit.

00:31:44.290 --> 00:31:46.180
He wants you to eat well, right?

00:31:46.570 --> 00:31:47.530
Yes, yes, Mom.

00:31:47.530 --> 00:31:49.330
Exactly. Your mom's right.

00:31:50.020 --> 00:31:51.290
Your wedding

00:31:51.670 --> 00:31:53.500
was far too simple.

00:31:56.850 --> 00:32:00.180
Even if we couldn't
afford a big banquet,

00:32:00.180 --> 00:32:03.700
you should at least hand out
some wedding candy.

00:32:03.700 --> 00:32:06.180
Let the neighbors
offer their blessings, right?

00:32:06.290 --> 00:32:08.100
Your father's right about that.

00:32:08.370 --> 00:32:09.980
Buy some wedding candy tomorrow.

00:32:09.980 --> 00:32:10.980
Bring it to the factory.

00:32:11.050 --> 00:32:12.180
Alright, I'll go buy it.

00:32:12.460 --> 00:32:14.370
Dad, Mom, it's really not necessary.

00:32:14.370 --> 00:32:15.740
Money should be spent wisely.

00:32:16.090 --> 00:32:17.330
We only get married once.

00:32:18.460 --> 00:32:19.570
You're the boss.

00:32:26.090 --> 00:32:26.800
This tastes great.

00:32:26.800 --> 00:32:27.780
Here, have more.

00:32:27.780 --> 00:32:28.660
That's enough.

00:32:28.660 --> 00:32:29.448
Stop piling it on.

00:32:29.471 --> 00:32:30.180
You two eat more.

00:32:30.180 --> 00:32:30.980
I also have some.

00:32:32.500 --> 00:32:34.330
Eat up.

00:32:47.510 --> 00:32:48.970
Double bed...

00:32:53.930 --> 00:32:56.460
Another chest of drawers?

00:32:57.570 --> 00:32:58.330
No, no.

00:32:58.330 --> 00:32:59.260
Too expensive.

00:32:59.800 --> 00:33:00.740
Let's just get a trunk.

00:33:10.530 --> 00:33:11.530
Have some water.

00:33:14.360 --> 00:33:15.570
Where did you get the money?

00:33:15.740 --> 00:33:17.460
I've been saving this for university

00:33:17.460 --> 00:33:19.130
since I started working.

00:33:19.420 --> 00:33:20.740
I scrimped every month

00:33:20.770 --> 00:33:21.740
to save this much.

00:33:23.020 --> 00:33:23.610
Right.

00:33:24.737 --> 00:33:25.850
And for today's groceries...

00:33:31.180 --> 00:33:32.700
I owe you an apology. I'm sorry.

00:33:32.810 --> 00:33:34.940
I got a little worked up at dinner.

00:33:34.980 --> 00:33:35.850
I shouldn't have.

00:33:36.290 --> 00:33:37.530
But, Fang Muyang...

00:33:42.370 --> 00:33:44.660
Even if this marriage is fake,

00:33:44.660 --> 00:33:46.850
the days we live together

00:33:46.850 --> 00:33:48.770
will be real.

00:33:49.660 --> 00:33:51.980
Every expense needs to be clear.

00:33:55.980 --> 00:33:58.460
At dinner just now,

00:33:58.460 --> 00:34:01.460
my parents and I all ate the meat.

00:34:01.460 --> 00:34:02.980
So take this money.

00:34:02.980 --> 00:34:04.980
Take it. Go on.

00:34:04.980 --> 00:34:05.740
Hold on to it.

00:34:06.330 --> 00:34:09.170
But if you keep spending
next month's money this month,

00:34:09.340 --> 00:34:11.980
and end up starving someday,
I'll have to feed you.

00:34:12.460 --> 00:34:13.860
So you're worried I'll starve?

00:34:14.530 --> 00:34:16.690
You really only hear half of what I say.

00:34:16.900 --> 00:34:19.250
I don't want to
support you if you starve.

00:34:30.900 --> 00:34:32.130
This is all the money I have.

00:34:32.860 --> 00:34:33.650
What for?

00:34:34.170 --> 00:34:35.530
You handle it from now on.

00:34:35.693 --> 00:34:36.690
I'm afraid I'll splurge.

00:34:37.210 --> 00:34:38.970
Alright. I'll keep it for now.

00:34:48.650 --> 00:34:50.210
Another 12 yuan from him...

00:34:58.170 --> 00:34:58.860
Students,

00:34:59.290 --> 00:35:00.380
outdoor sketching

00:35:00.380 --> 00:35:01.550
is the most important course

00:35:01.980 --> 00:35:03.900
at our newspaper's
Worker-Peasant-Soldier

00:35:04.170 --> 00:35:05.380
Art Training School.

00:35:06.470 --> 00:35:07.570
When it comes to painting,

00:35:08.090 --> 00:35:10.420
the worst you can do
is shut yourself in.

00:35:11.360 --> 00:35:12.620
Nature

00:35:13.020 --> 00:35:14.610
is our best teacher.

00:35:15.730 --> 00:35:16.480
What are you doing?

00:35:16.690 --> 00:35:17.690
Stop! Don't run!

00:35:18.570 --> 00:35:20.570
That's stealing from socialist property!

00:35:21.690 --> 00:35:22.530
Stop running!

00:35:25.130 --> 00:35:27.690
Qiang, are there really fish here?

00:35:29.170 --> 00:35:32.130
Yeah. Plenty of fish in there.

00:35:32.340 --> 00:35:34.460
But the patrol team
won't let them fish.

00:35:34.780 --> 00:35:36.650
So they sneak over.

00:35:37.500 --> 00:35:38.900
Focus on your sketching.

00:35:39.300 --> 00:35:40.500
No whispering.

00:35:44.460 --> 00:35:47.530
(Jiangnan Municipal People's Hospital)

00:35:47.530 --> 00:35:48.780
Doctor, how did it go?

00:35:49.530 --> 00:35:50.780
The surgery was a success.

00:35:50.780 --> 00:35:51.690
(Operating Room)

00:35:51.690 --> 00:35:54.170
Dong, brief the family on post-op care.

00:35:54.170 --> 00:35:55.690
Alright. Please come this way.

00:36:28.848 --> 00:36:29.900
What are you doing here?

00:36:31.090 --> 00:36:31.940
Mom said

00:36:32.340 --> 00:36:34.340
you're drenched in sweat
after every surgery.

00:36:35.250 --> 00:36:37.340
I brought you a change of clothes.

00:36:37.570 --> 00:36:38.690
Consider it

00:36:39.420 --> 00:36:40.860
a wife's duty.

00:36:45.940 --> 00:36:47.130
I never noticed before,

00:36:47.780 --> 00:36:49.380
but that color looks great on you.

00:36:53.648 --> 00:36:55.050
I didn't dare wear it before.

00:36:55.271 --> 00:36:58.071
I was afraid people would say
I still carried bourgeois habits.

00:36:58.293 --> 00:37:00.340
With the wrong background,
even beauty is a crime.

00:37:01.170 --> 00:37:02.340
But I'm not afraid anymore.

00:37:05.570 --> 00:37:06.210
Here.

00:37:09.182 --> 00:37:10.020
Let's eat together.

00:37:10.493 --> 00:37:12.340
I can't.
I've got school things to handle.

00:37:24.300 --> 00:37:27.460
(Jiangcheng Vintage Store)

00:37:42.530 --> 00:37:43.340
Fei Ni,

00:37:44.780 --> 00:37:46.170
we're newlyweds.

00:37:46.650 --> 00:37:48.170
Should we buy secondhand furniture?

00:37:48.500 --> 00:37:49.980
If new furniture is too expensive,

00:37:50.130 --> 00:37:51.250
we could buy some lumber.

00:37:51.530 --> 00:37:52.500
I can build it myself.

00:37:53.130 --> 00:37:54.300
What's wrong with secondhand?

00:37:54.730 --> 00:37:56.250
It looks perfectly fine to me.

00:37:59.050 --> 00:38:00.170
Look at this bed.

00:38:00.690 --> 00:38:01.780
I think it's great.

00:38:02.460 --> 00:38:03.650
One each.

00:38:04.660 --> 00:38:05.280
I...

00:38:12.170 --> 00:38:13.170
We're married.

00:38:13.350 --> 00:38:15.280
How can we each sleep in a single bed?

00:38:15.980 --> 00:38:17.740
The neighbors would
know something's off.

00:38:18.730 --> 00:38:20.160
And what about your parents?

00:38:21.530 --> 00:38:22.340
Besides,

00:38:22.340 --> 00:38:23.690
our place is tiny.

00:38:23.780 --> 00:38:25.382
Where would we even fit two single beds?

00:38:26.870 --> 00:38:27.620
True.

00:38:29.080 --> 00:38:29.870
This one's nice.

00:38:32.980 --> 00:38:33.980
This double bed is good.

00:38:35.170 --> 00:38:36.340
No way.

00:38:36.380 --> 00:38:37.070
If we buy that,

00:38:37.070 --> 00:38:38.690
I'll have to sleep
next to you every day.

00:38:42.040 --> 00:38:44.100
That's what married people do.

00:38:46.890 --> 00:38:47.970
Don't forget

00:38:48.610 --> 00:38:50.360
what you said on our wedding day.

00:38:50.650 --> 00:38:52.470
One big bed divided into two.

00:38:52.660 --> 00:38:54.150
We have to sleep separately.

00:38:56.500 --> 00:38:57.380
Then I can't help it.

00:38:58.000 --> 00:38:59.940
There's no space
for two single beds anyway.

00:39:11.250 --> 00:39:12.340
This one's good.

00:39:12.730 --> 00:39:14.020
A bunk bed.

00:39:14.460 --> 00:39:16.130
One bunk each.

00:39:16.380 --> 00:39:18.460
If anyone asks,

00:39:19.130 --> 00:39:20.690
we'll say the top is for storage.

00:39:22.420 --> 00:39:23.780
Then, it'll look like a dorm.

00:39:24.530 --> 00:39:25.650
So what?

00:39:25.730 --> 00:39:26.690
It's our home.

00:39:26.690 --> 00:39:27.980
I'll put whatever I want in it.

00:39:31.170 --> 00:39:33.090
Why don't we need a desk anymore?

00:39:33.340 --> 00:39:34.900
You said on our wedding day

00:39:34.900 --> 00:39:36.130
that we had to get one.

00:39:36.940 --> 00:39:38.170
It's too expensive.

00:39:38.380 --> 00:39:39.570
This trunk is better.

00:39:39.900 --> 00:39:40.900
It can be a table,

00:39:40.900 --> 00:39:41.980
and store things, too.

00:39:41.980 --> 00:39:43.090
That's practical.

00:39:43.090 --> 00:39:43.980
It's ugly.

00:39:43.980 --> 00:39:45.250
It's not even proper furniture.

00:39:45.250 --> 00:39:46.340
Who cares if it's ugly?

00:39:46.340 --> 00:39:47.650
- Look...
- As long as it works.

00:39:50.448 --> 00:39:51.404
I've got an idea.

00:39:52.340 --> 00:39:55.210
Let's buy both the trunk and the desk.

00:39:56.340 --> 00:39:56.810
No way.

00:39:56.810 --> 00:39:57.730
Hear me out.

00:39:57.730 --> 00:39:59.980
The trunk can store things

00:40:00.170 --> 00:40:01.300
and be a dining table.

00:40:01.500 --> 00:40:03.980
The desk can hold books for studying

00:40:04.050 --> 00:40:05.250
and double as a nightstand.

00:40:05.300 --> 00:40:07.130
Two pieces, four uses.

00:40:07.530 --> 00:40:08.860
That's real practicality.

00:40:11.900 --> 00:40:12.420
Alright.

00:40:12.980 --> 00:40:13.820
Move it in!

00:40:14.204 --> 00:40:15.210
Careful, you'll hit it!

00:40:18.871 --> 00:40:20.130
Didn't I say don't touch it?

00:40:20.130 --> 00:40:20.690
I've got it.

00:40:20.690 --> 00:40:21.380
It's fine.

00:40:22.460 --> 00:40:23.080
Dad, Mom.

00:40:23.080 --> 00:40:25.182
- I'll go fetch some water.
- Dad, take it slow.

00:40:26.730 --> 00:40:29.050
You hardly have anything in this place.

00:40:29.460 --> 00:40:32.340
I told you to bring
that cabinet from our house,

00:40:32.500 --> 00:40:33.460
but you refused.

00:40:33.860 --> 00:40:34.340
Mom,

00:40:34.340 --> 00:40:36.570
it's just the two of us.
We don't need much.

00:40:36.780 --> 00:40:38.210
Besides, didn't I already bring

00:40:38.210 --> 00:40:39.300
the sewing machine?

00:40:39.690 --> 00:40:40.170
It's enough.

00:40:40.380 --> 00:40:42.050
You just hate spending money.

00:40:42.050 --> 00:40:43.300
You think I don't know you?

00:40:43.900 --> 00:40:45.530
Don't scrimp on the money

00:40:45.530 --> 00:40:46.530
we gave you.

00:40:46.780 --> 00:40:47.780
I know.

00:40:47.780 --> 00:40:49.650
We'll get everything sorted soon.

00:40:49.650 --> 00:40:50.730
Don't worry.

00:40:51.300 --> 00:40:51.900
Ni,

00:40:52.380 --> 00:40:53.780
putting everything else aside,

00:40:53.980 --> 00:40:55.250
this bunk bed of yours

00:40:55.250 --> 00:40:57.210
looks just like a dorm.

00:40:58.380 --> 00:41:00.780
Dad, it's creative.

00:41:00.820 --> 00:41:02.170
A bunk bed,

00:41:02.170 --> 00:41:04.250
the top bunk can store things.
Isn't that great?

00:41:05.460 --> 00:41:06.530
Fine.

00:41:08.210 --> 00:41:09.530
It looks strange to me.

00:41:09.604 --> 00:41:10.980
It's not like a couple's room.

00:41:13.340 --> 00:41:14.780
We just got married.

00:41:14.780 --> 00:41:16.340
Practicality comes first.

00:41:16.650 --> 00:41:17.340
By the way,

00:41:17.650 --> 00:41:18.380
Dad, Mom,

00:41:18.380 --> 00:41:20.170
my brother's coming back tomorrow.

00:41:20.380 --> 00:41:21.650
You should start preparing

00:41:21.650 --> 00:41:23.690
for his wedding with Lin Mei.

00:41:23.780 --> 00:41:25.650
Focus your energy on them.

00:41:25.690 --> 00:41:27.050
Don't worry about us.

00:41:27.380 --> 00:41:28.250
Right, Dad.

00:41:28.315 --> 00:41:29.650
I'll change the water for you.

00:41:41.860 --> 00:41:44.780
Honey, stop sighing all the time.

00:41:45.900 --> 00:41:46.650
It's fine.

00:41:46.650 --> 00:41:49.530
As long as the two of them
live well together,

00:41:49.530 --> 00:41:50.690
that's what matters most.

00:41:50.980 --> 00:41:52.300
No need to worry over nothing.

00:41:52.300 --> 00:41:53.380
Dad, Mom, have some water.

00:41:55.090 --> 00:41:55.980
No, no.

00:41:55.980 --> 00:41:56.980
Just leave it there.

00:41:57.460 --> 00:41:58.730
Come here.

00:41:58.730 --> 00:42:00.130
Help me stick this up.

00:42:00.130 --> 00:42:00.780
Okay.

00:42:00.940 --> 00:42:03.730
(Double-Happiness)
There, that side's done.

00:42:04.170 --> 00:42:05.380
A little higher on that side.

00:42:05.570 --> 00:42:06.730
Higher?

00:42:06.730 --> 00:42:07.650
Yes, just a bit.

00:42:22.500 --> 00:42:23.280
Comrade Fei Ni,

00:42:23.900 --> 00:42:25.260
top bunk or bottom bunk?

00:42:26.730 --> 00:42:28.050
I picked the bed.

00:42:28.170 --> 00:42:28.730
You choose.

00:42:28.730 --> 00:42:29.760
I'm fine either way.

00:42:31.650 --> 00:42:32.980
You should take the top.

00:42:33.050 --> 00:42:34.090
It's cleaner, for one.

00:42:34.530 --> 00:42:35.900
And I can't hold my liquor.

00:42:35.900 --> 00:42:37.860
If I ever get drunk with your dad,

00:42:38.115 --> 00:42:39.648
I might crawl into the wrong bed.

00:42:39.780 --> 00:42:40.570
I'll take the top.

00:42:42.130 --> 00:42:42.940
Deal.

00:42:44.780 --> 00:42:45.570
Coming!

00:42:49.650 --> 00:42:50.380
Chief Wang.

00:42:50.380 --> 00:42:52.460
Fei Ni, who would've thought
we'd be neighbors?

00:42:52.460 --> 00:42:52.860
Right.

00:42:53.380 --> 00:42:54.300
Hello, Fang.

00:42:54.300 --> 00:42:55.760
- Have an apple.
- Hello, Chief Wang.

00:42:55.782 --> 00:42:56.737
Thank you, Chief Wang.

00:42:56.737 --> 00:42:57.337
Hello.

00:42:58.210 --> 00:42:59.940
Such a big painting.

00:43:00.980 --> 00:43:02.530
Nice, very nice.

00:43:03.250 --> 00:43:04.570
Young people are full of

00:43:04.570 --> 00:43:05.340
different ideas.

00:43:10.210 --> 00:43:11.860
You two are not sleeping together?

00:43:28.860 --> 00:43:33.340
♪After the laughter, I think of you♪

00:43:35.900 --> 00:43:40.620
♪After the storm, I think of you♪

00:43:43.140 --> 00:43:49.260
♪In the little courtyard,
there you are dancing♪

00:43:50.260 --> 00:43:54.820
♪That earnest you,
smiling so innocently♪

00:43:57.300 --> 00:44:02.060
♪In spring, I stay by your side♪

00:44:04.500 --> 00:44:08.860
♪When summer comes, I watch over you♪

00:44:11.220 --> 00:44:17.860
♪In the light of dawn, you belong to me♪

00:44:17.860 --> 00:44:27.460
♪At the edge of the world,
I will still hold you tight♪

00:44:28.540 --> 00:44:34.700
♪There is a small place♪

00:44:34.700 --> 00:44:41.500
♪Where they carry big dreams♪

00:44:41.500 --> 00:44:48.860
♪Every lovely face♪

00:44:49.740 --> 00:44:55.900
♪Shines brightly in the heart♪

00:44:56.700 --> 00:45:02.740
♪Even when we collide,
we hold our course♪

00:45:03.940 --> 00:45:09.740
♪Even when we stumble,
we keep our resolve♪

00:45:10.820 --> 00:45:17.100
♪My you, walking toward the distance♪

00:45:17.900 --> 00:45:26.140
♪Please carry our dreams
and let them soar♪